<h4 id="tilt"><span style="color: #EBD9A4">Obliquity</span></h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="6u 12u$(mobile)">
    <img src="{{ 'assets/images/research_1.png' | relative_url }}" alt="Arthur's face" class="image fit"/>
  </div>
  <div class="6u 12u$(mobile)">
    <span style="color: #EBD9A4">
      My research centers on learning more about planets outside our Solar System by observing their phases as they orbit their host stars. Their thermal profile translates to these phases and tells us about how these planets respond to the heating from the stars.
    </span>
  </div>
</div>

